title: Andre Rieu - Magic of the violin CD 320k (musicfromrizzo) Orchst
description:
Andre Rieu - Magic of the violin CD 320k (musicfromrizzo)

Here is the incomparable, the great Monsieur Andre Rieu of Europe for you with
the Johnann Strauss Orchestra too including some lovely backup singers / chorus.

Includes one of my most favourite violin pieces "Winter - from Vivaldi's Fiour seasons' I also love Bach's Brandenburg concertos for violin although that ins't on here

Fans of Ave maria won't be disappointed either.

enjoy and please seed
Michael Rizzo Chessman
